model.name: Kawka2014 - Revealing the role of SGK1 in the dynamics of medulloblastoma using a mathematical model

body.pre: This is a mathematical model of the Wnt signaling pathway in medulloblastoma comprised of two compartments. Composed of nine ordinary differential equations accounts for the formation and dissociation of complexes as well as the transcription, translation and transportation between the cytoplasm and the nucleus.
